I am also having an issue with conditional formatting.  I am trying to apply a fill to cells that contain 'X' and it is not working.

Here is my code:

```
    sheet.addConditionalFormatting({
      ref: 'A1:A26',
      rules: [
        {
          type: 'containsText',
          operator: 'containsText',
          text: 'X',
          style: {
            fill: {
              type: 'pattern',
              pattern: 'solid',
              bgColor: { argb: 'FF00FF00' }
            }
          }
        }
      ]
